00:44:05,220 --> 00:44:07,900
 On želi uči v naše svakodnevne situacije,

586
00:44:07,900 --> 00:44:11,060
 v naše obiteljske odnose,

587
00:44:11,060 --> 00:44:12,900
 v naše financijske probleme,

588
00:44:12,900 --> 00:44:15,540
 v sve stvari.

589
00:44:16,060 --> 00:44:17,840
 Onda sam pitao patra Mihovila,

590
00:44:17,840 --> 00:44:18,440
 pa dobro, ok,

591
00:44:18,440 --> 00:44:20,500
 pa zašto me je gospodin deset godina,

592
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:22,100
 jedanest godina smo patili,

593
00:44:22,100 --> 00:44:24,220
 da smo došli do toga.

594
00:44:24,220 --> 00:44:27,020
 Ali Bog uvijek ima plan.

595
00:44:27,020 --> 00:44:28,760
 On kaže meni,

596
00:44:28,760 --> 00:44:30,000
 pogrešno pitanje.

597
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,720
 Šta pogrešno pitanje?

598
00:44:31,720 --> 00:44:32,580
 On kaže,

599
00:44:32,580 --> 00:44:34,160
 gospodin je znao,

600
00:44:34,160 --> 00:44:35,640
 da ćete vi doći,

601
00:44:35,640 --> 00:44:37,400
 vaša obitelj u to kuću,

602
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:40,060
 i da vi možete spasiti ove duše,

603
00:44:40,060 --> 00:44:41,660
 koji su napravljali ove grijehe.

604
00:44:41,660 --> 00:44:45,860
 Znači, to je čin najvećeg Božeg milosrđa.

605
00:44:45,860 --> 00:44:47,500
 Što je rekao,

606
00:44:47,500 --> 00:44:48,780
 o, dobro se to čuje.

607
00:44:48,780 --> 00:44:51,540
 Znači, gospodin ima uvek plan

608
00:44:51,540 --> 00:44:52,940
 u teškim situacijama

609
00:44:52,940 --> 00:44:55,120
 i ništa mu je nije teško.

610
00:44:55,120 --> 00:44:58,520
 Na kraju samo jedna poruka

611
00:44:58,520 --> 00:44:59,500
 za sve nas.

612
00:44:59,500 --> 00:45:03,580
 Znači, gospodin

613
00:45:03,580 --> 00:45:06,040
 u svim našim problemima,

614
00:45:06,040 --> 00:45:07,760
 u svim našim situacijama

615
00:45:07,760 --> 00:45:09,840
 želi biti prisutan.

616
00:45:09,840 --> 00:45:13,160
 I naš zadatak je,

617
00:45:13,160 --> 00:45:15,320
 da gospodina pozovemo u sve to

618
00:45:15,320 --> 00:45:17,580
 i da mu sve predajemo,

619
00:45:17,580 --> 00:45:20,560
 da on upravlja našim životom,

620
00:45:20,560 --> 00:45:21,160
 našim situacijam.

621
00:45:21,900 --> 00:45:23,080
 Ne kao da sam ja rekao,

622
00:45:23,080 --> 00:45:25,020
 gospodin, budi ti pored mene,

623
00:45:25,020 --> 00:45:27,420
 nego, gospodin, ti vozi auto,

624
00:45:27,420 --> 00:45:28,860
 ti ideš za volan,

625
00:45:28,860 --> 00:45:30,400
 a ja ću biti pored tebe.

626
00:45:30,400 --> 00:45:35,720
 I onda dođe blagoslov i rješenje.

627
00:45:35,720 --> 00:45:40,600
 I sada tražio sam, znači,

628
00:45:40,600 --> 00:45:42,540
 duhovne ljude koji su mi pomogli,

629
00:45:42,540 --> 00:45:44,000
 dali su mi savjete.

630
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:48,620
 I sada me gospodin koristi,

631
00:45:48,620 --> 00:45:50,020
 već me je počeo koristiti,

632
00:45:50,020 --> 00:45:51,820
 da u sličnim situacijama

633
00:45:51,820 --> 00:45:54,060
 sam počeo pomagati drugima.

634
00:45:54,060 --> 00:45:56,840
 Blagoslovljati druge.

635
00:45:56,840 --> 00:45:58,740
 Jer gospodin kaže,

636
00:45:58,740 --> 00:46:01,100
 da brez njega ne možemo ništa napraviti.

637
00:46:01,100 --> 00:46:02,620
 Gospodin ne kaže,

638
00:46:02,620 --> 00:46:04,800
 bez mene ne možete malo napraviti.

639
00:46:04,800 --> 00:46:05,600
 Ništa.

640
00:46:05,600 --> 00:46:08,040
 I tako nekaj bude.

641
00:46:08,040 --> 00:46:08,840
 Amen.

642
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:46,980
 Hvala što pratite kanal.

